                $.extend(kendo.ui.WeekView.fn, {
                    calculateDateRange: function () {
                        var selectedDate = this.options.date,
                            firstDay = kendo.culture().calendar.firstDay,
                            start = kendo.date.dayOfWeek(selectedDate, firstDay, -1),
                            idx, length,
                            dates = [];
        
                        for (idx = 0, length = 7; idx < length; idx++) {
                            dates.push(start);
                            start = kendo.date.nextDay(start);
                        }
                        this._render(dates);
                    }
                });
        
                kendo.culture("en-NZ");

                    $("#staffSearch").keypress(function(event){
                        var code = event.keyCode;  // getting ASCII code for the pressed key
        
                        //Upper case A-Z == ASCII 65-90 , Lower case a-z == ASCII 97-122, space==32 , Enter==13
                        if((code >= 65 && code <=90) || (code >= 97 && code <= 122) || (code == 32) || (code == 13))
                        {
                            selectedJobId = null;
                            searchStaffs($(this).val());
                        }
        
                        else
                        {
                            alert("Accept Alphanumeric Characters and space only");
                        }
                    });

                function showJobDetailWindow(jobId){
        
                    $(document.body).append('<div id="detailWindow"></div>');
        
                    var title = "";
        
        
                    var actionUrl = "";
        
                    if (jobId == 0) {
                        actionUrl = createJobUrl;
                        title = "Create Job";
                    } else {
                        actionUrl = editJobUrl + "?id=" + jobId;
                        title = "Edit Job";
                    }
        
                    windowElement = $("#detailWindow").kendoWindow({
                        title: title,
                        content: actionUrl,
                        iframe: true,
                        actions: ["Close"],
                        modal: true,
                        resizable: false,
                        draggable: true,
                        width: 900,
                        height: 800,
                        //scrollable: true,
                        close: function (e) {
                        }
                    });
        
                    var detailWindow = $("#detailWindow").data("kendoWindow");
        
                    detailWindow.center().open();
                }
        
                function showUserDetailWindow(userId){
                    $(document.body).append('<div id="detailWindow"></div>');
        
                    var title = "";
        
        
                    var actionUrl = "";
        
                    if (userId == 0) {
                        return;
                    } else {
                        actionUrl = editUserUrl + "?id=" + userId+"&withHeader=false";
                        title = "Edit User";
                    }
        
                    windowElement = $("#detailWindow").kendoWindow({
                        title: title,
                        content: actionUrl,
                        iframe: true,
                        actions: ["Close"],
                        modal: true,
                        resizable: false,
                        draggable: true,
                        width: 900,
                        height: 800,
                        //scrollable: true,
                        close: function (e) {
                        }
                    });
        
                    var detailWindow = $("#detailWindow").data("kendoWindow");
        
                    detailWindow.center().open();
                }

                function objectsAreSame(x, y) {
                    var objectsAreSame = true;
                    for(var propertyName in x) {
                        if(x[propertyName] !== y[propertyName]) {
                            objectsAreSame = false;
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                    return objectsAreSame;
                }
        
                var previousRecentEvents = null;
                function RefreshRecentEvents(){
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "POST",
                        url:companyAuditUrl,
                        success:function(result){
                            $('#eventlines').html(result);
                            if(previousRecentEvents != null){
                                var firstInNew = $(result).find(".auditInfo:first-child div:first-child").text();
                                var firstInOld = $(previousRecentEvents).find(".auditInfo:first-child  div:first-child").text();
                                console.log(firstInNew);
                                console.log(firstInOld);
                                if (firstInNew != firstInOld) {
                                    audio.play();
                                    $(".jobAudit").effect("highlight", {}, 3000);
                                }
                            }
        
                            previousRecentEvents = result;
                        }
                    });
                }
        
                function ShowJobOnMap(jobId){
                    for(var i = 0; i <markersArray.length; i++){
                        var marker = markersArray[i];
        
                        var tmpJobId = marker.get("jobId");
                        if(tmpJobId == jobId){
                            var lat = marker.get("lat");
                            var long = marker.get("long");
        
                            map.setZoom(18);
                            map.panTo( new google.maps.LatLng(lat, long));
                        }
                    }
                }

                function sortUnorderedList(ul, sortDescending) {
        
                    if(typeof ul == "string")
                        ul = document.getElementById(ul);
                    var lis;
                    debugger;
                    if (ul==document.getElementById('jobBoxes'))
                        lis = ul.getElementsByClassName('job');
                    else  lis = ul.getElementsByClassName('staff');
                    var vals = [];
        
                    for(var i = 0, l = lis.length; i < l; i++)
                        vals.push(lis[i].innerHTML);
        
                    vals.sort();
        
                    if(sortDescending)
                        vals.reverse();
        
                    for(var i = 0, l = lis.length; i < l; i++)
                        lis[i].innerHTML = vals[i];
                }

               * The CenterControl adds a control to the map that recenters the map on

               * This constructor takes the control DIV as an argument.

                function CenterControl(controlDiv, map) {
        
                    // Set CSS for the control border.
                    var controlUI = document.createElement('div');
                    controlUI.style.backgroundColor = '#fff';
                    controlUI.style.border = '2px solid #fff';
                    controlUI.style.borderRadius = '3px';
                    controlUI.style.boxShadow = '0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.3)';
                    controlUI.style.cursor = 'pointer';
                    controlUI.style.marginTop = '10px';
                    controlUI.style.textAlign = 'center';
                    controlUI.title = 'Delete all markers';
                    controlDiv.appendChild(controlUI);
        
                    // Set CSS for the control interior.
                    var controlText = document.createElement('div');
                    controlText.style.color = 'rgb(25,25,25)';
                    controlText.style.fontFamily = 'Roboto,Arial,sans-serif';
                    controlText.style.fontSize = '16px';
                    controlText.style.lineHeight = '28px';
                    controlText.style.paddingLeft = '5px';
                    controlText.style.paddingRight = '5px';
                    controlText.innerHTML = 'Delete Markers';
                    controlUI.appendChild(controlText);
        
                    // Setup the click event listeners: simply set the map to Chicago.
                    controlUI.addEventListener('click', function() {
                        DeleteAllMarkers();
                    });
        
                }

                $.extend(kendo.ui.WeekView.fn, {
                    calculateDateRange: function () {
                        var selectedDate = this.options.date,
                            firstDay = kendo.culture().calendar.firstDay,
                            start = kendo.date.dayOfWeek(selectedDate, firstDay, -1),
                            idx, length,
                            dates = [];

                            dates.push(start);
                            start = kendo.date.nextDay(start);
                        }

                    }
